metadata.name: 1WS #0001/1024
metadata.description:
Lifetime membership to One White Square, one of only 1024. Can be kept, sold, transferred and gifted - only the holder has membership. There will only ever be 1024 squares.

Allows the holder entry to the metaverse's most exclusive private members club, including club spaces, special partner benefits, exclusive NFT drops, our members community and more.
